{
  /**
   * DESIGN DECISION: Dependency Strategy
   * 
   * This package.json reflects a minimal, purposeful dependency philosophy:
   * 
   * Production Dependencies (Keep Runtime Lean):
   * 
   * 1. **@google/generative-ai**: Official Gemini SDK
   *    Why: Type-safe AI integration, function calling support, streaming
   *    Alternative considered: OpenAI SDK (rejected: Gemini has better function calling)
   * 
   * 2. **idb**: IndexedDB wrapper
   *    Why: Promise-based API, TypeScript types, tiny (~3KB)
   *    Current status: Prepared for future migration, not actively used
   *    Alternative: Raw IndexedDB API (rejected: verbose, error-prone)
   * 
   * 3. **react + react-dom**: UI framework
   *    Version 19.2.x (latest major)
   *    Why: Virtual DOM diffing, component model, ecosystem
   * 
   * 4. **react-markdown**: Markdown rendering
   *    Why: AI responses use markdown (bold, lists, code blocks)
   *    Alternative: Dangerously setting innerHTML (rejected: XSS risk)
   * 
   * Development Dependencies:
   * 
   * 5. **tailwindcss + plugins**: Utility-first CSS
   *    Why: Rapid prototyping, consistent design system, tree-shakeable
   * 
   * 6. **vite**: Build tool
   *    Why: Fast HMR (~50ms), ES modules, minimal config
   *    Alternative: Create React App (rejected: slow, opinionated)
   * 
   * 7. **typescript**: Type safety
   *    Why: Catch errors at compile time, better IDE support
   *    Version: ~5.8.2 (tilde = accept patches, not minors)
   * 
   * Notably Absent:
   * - No state management (Redux, Zustand): Props drilling sufficient at this scale
   * - No routing (React Router): Single-page app with view state
   * - No form library (Formik, React Hook Form): Simple inline forms
   * - No test framework: Manual testing sufficient for MVP (future: Vitest)
   * 
   * Philosophy: Add dependencies when pain justifies complexity, not preemptively.
   */
  "name": "life-orchestrator",
  "private": true,
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "vite",
    "build": "vite build",
    "preview": "vite preview"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@google/generative-ai": "^0.24.1",
    "idb": "^8.0.3",
    "react": "^19.2.3",
    "react-dom": "^19.2.4",
    "react-markdown": "9.0.1"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@tailwindcss/typography": "^0.5.19",
    "@types/node": "^22.14.0",
    "@vitejs/plugin-react": "^5.0.0",
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.24",
    "postcss": "^8.5.6",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.4.17",
    "typescript": "~5.8.2",
    "vite": "^6.2.0"
  }
}
